                <div class="faq-answer">For Class 11th, candidate must have passed Class 10th from a recognized board with minimum 45% marks. For Class 12th, candidate must have passed Class 11th from a recognized institution.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
                <div class="faq-question"><span>Is there any entrance exam?</span><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
                <div class="faq-answer">Yes, there is a written entrance test followed by a personal interview for all courses. The test assesses basic knowledge in core subjects.</div>
